# ACCESSING/PROCESSING DRAKKAR FILES

1) ./get_drakkar
# Access the Rutgers ESM computer for original drakkar files
# NOTE: these file are already "drowned" by SOSIE

2) ./prelim_file_edit 
# Sorts files by year and changes the record dimension name to 'time'
# NOTE: only run once

3) ./make_DFS5.3_roms_clim
# Creates monthly climatologies for the years of interest
# NOTE: the 3-hrly fields start at hr 3 of a given day and end
#       with midnight of the next; always 8 time vals per day 
